data.description: Welcome home to this charming like-new 3 bed, 2 bath property located in a desirable area! The living room is spacious and perfect for entertaining, with plenty of natural light flowing in. The bedrooms are cozy and comfortable, with ample closet space. Step outside and take in the large yard, perfect for outdoor activities and gardening. The location of this property is unbeatable, with easy access to local shops, restaurants, and entertainment options. All Kitchen Appliances and Washer & Dryer Remain. 10x12 Outbuilding Remains. 24"x 54" Above Ground Pool and Equipment Remains. PES Internet currently, Spectrum also available. Don't miss your chance to own this wonderful home - schedule a showing today!
